data.description: Imagine sitting on your spacious screened lanai relaxing in your private backyard, entertaining friends, or enjoying the quiet. Low HOA Fees, natural gas, & beautiful amenities are a plus in this Northern St. Johns County neighborhood with 'A' rated schools & convenient access to I-95. Featuring an open concept main living area, extended finished garage, designated office space, plenty of extra closet space, & sizable downstairs master suite with two walk-in closets, double sinks, a large shower. Dual HVAC systems ensure both downstairs & upstairs stay cool & comfortable. Located in The Grove at Bannon Lakes, this impeccably maintained home on .37 acres backs up to a preserve and has plenty of room for a pool. Don't be surprised if a lovely little deer stops by to say hello.
